listings.public_title: $118.2K Per Month Subscription-Box Site in the Culinary Niche
listings.summary:
This listing is for a subscription-box business created in July 2015 in the culinary niche. The Cratejoy store features a subscription box product containing foods, utensils, and recipes for a particular type of cuisine. The store sells some award-winning products and it has been featured on big media brands in the niche including Men's Health. The business requires minimal effort from the Seller to maintain.

The business uses a 3PL to fulfill orders and currently has 100+ US-based suppliers. A number of freelancers help to run the business, including a Customer Service Agent, a Social Media Manager, a Writer, and a Developer.

The business currently has 3,125 subscribers to the product. The subscriptions offered are monthly, 3-month, 6-month, and 12-month subscriptions. The average revenue per customer is $162.58. With the subscription, customers get access to an online community that features a news feed and video content related to the niche. Some t-shirt sales are also made.

Included in the sale are four branded domains, an email list of 55,000 subscribers, a large social following including a Facebook account with 33K+ followers which gets decent levels of engagement, and an Instagram account with 84K+ subscribers which gets high levels of engagement. There is an automated email funnel set up for customers that sends welcome emails and informative emails each week.
assets_included: 4 Domains including all content and files for the sites
Social media accounts (Facebook, Twitter, Instagram, Pinterest)
opportunities: Growing and monetizing the email list
risks: Supplier/factory changing terms of agreement or unable to produce product to meet demand
Google algorithmic changes could cause traffic to fluctuate
listings.seller_support: The Seller is willing to offer 60 days of email support and 2 Skype calls to ensure a smooth transition of the sale. This is twice the amount of support usually offered by a Seller.
listings.reason_for_sale: The Seller would like the time to focus on other projects.
work_required: Overseeing the work of the contractors
Working on bulk sales and collaborations
